-> register, login

room
- number capacity type price features
-> add show update delete

customer
- name phone personal_details
-> add show update delete

booking
- customer room check_in_date check_out_date
-> add show update delete

service
- name details charge
-> add show update delete

items
- name type price
-> add show update delete

bill
- bill_no customer (booking service items) date approved_by sc discount vat


